==== POS-Tech Web ====

This part is a web extension of the base POS-Tech. It must be deployed along it
but stays independant.

== Installation and configuration ==

-- Web server configuration --

Configure our web server to point to the htdocs and api directories.

The first one is the web back office, the second one is an http remote API
required for optional clients like the Android client.

-- Site configuration

Copy config.php.sample to config.php and set the values according to your
POS-Tech configuration.

